05:03.040 --> 05:04.040
Pengarah Wang, saya tiada.

05:04.040 --> 05:04.640
Berambus!

05:05.680 --> 05:06.240
Pengarah Wang.

05:06.240 --> 05:06.840
Berambus!

05:07.240 --> 05:08.430
Kalau awak tak mampu bayar pampasan,

05:08.430 --> 05:10.160
