06:37.510 --> 06:38.950
Mak long, janganlah marah dia.

06:38.950 --> 06:40.240
Geramnya saya.

06:45.159 --> 06:45.830
Xiaolan.

06:46.190 --> 06:46.750
Xiaolan.

06:47.120 --> 06:48.430
Xiaolan, awak tak boleh keluar!

06:48.430 --> 06:49.800
Geramnya saya.

06:50.560 --> 06:51.159
Apa yang berlaku ini?

06:51.159 --> 06:52.430
Bukankah itu Xia Xiaolan

06:52.430 --> 06:53.490
